ence\": \"The main culprit, according to some experts, is increasing pressure.\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 3015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The main culprit\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 2963}, {\"ngram\": \"some experts\", \"from\": 2978, \"to\": 2990}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3014}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Young athletes start earlier and spend more time training than in the past.\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3091, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Young athletes\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3030}, {\"ngram\": \"more time training\", \"from\": 3055, \"to\": 3073}, {\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 3082, \"to\": 3090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More money is at stake too: Sponsors reward success even in obscure sports such as handball and artistic swimming, and many athletes make an income asinfluencers.\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"More money\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3102}, {\"ngram\": \"stake\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3114}, {\"ngram\": \"Sponsors\", \"from\": 3120, \"to\": 3128}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3143}, {\"ngram\": \"obscure sports\", \"from\": 3152, \"to\": 3166}, {\"ngram\": \"handball\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3183}, {\"ngram\": \"artistic swimming\", \"from\": 3188, \"to\": 3205}, {\"ngram\": \"many athletes\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3224}, {\"ngram\": \"an income asinfluencers\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A number of countries pay their Olympic athletes, with big bonuses for medaling.\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3335, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A number\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3263}, {\"ngram\": \"countries\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3276}, {\"ngram\": \"their Olympic athletes\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3303}, {\"ngram\": \"big bonuses\", \"from\": 3310, \"to\": 3321}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Losing the gold can mean losing gold.\", \"from\": 3336, \"to\": 3373, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 3343, \"to\": 3351}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 3368, \"to\": 3372}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boorish athletes might also be reacting to growing amounts of attention.\", \"from\": 3375, \"to\": 3447, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Boorish athletes\", \"from\": 3375, \"to\": 3391}, {\"ngram\": \"growing amounts\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3433}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 3437, \"to\": 3446}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stephen Garcia, a psychologist at the University of Michigan who studies competition, told me that athletes often suffer \\\"evaluation apprehension\\\" based on the number of people watching them.\", \"from\": 3448, \"to\": 3639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3448, \"end\": 3462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Garcia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stephen Garcia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Garcia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Garcia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a psychologist\", \"from\": 3464, \"to\": 3478}, {\"ngram\": \"the University\", \"from\": 3482, \"to\": 3496}, {\"ngram\": \"Michigan\", \"from\": 3500, \"to\": 3508}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 3521, \"to\": 3532}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3547, \"to\": 3555}, {\"ngram\": \"evaluation apprehension\", \"from\": 3570, \"to\": 3593}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 3604, \"to\": 3614}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3618, \"to\": 3624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bigger the audience, the more stress they feel.\", \"from\": 3640, \"to\": 3691, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The bigger the audience\", \"from\": 3640, \"to\": 3663}, {\"ngram\": \"the more stress\", \"from\": 3665, \"to\": 3680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now that anyone with a phone can broadcast an event in real time, and highlights (and lowlights) live on in social-media feeds, the feeling of being watched is more powerful than ever, Garcia said.\", \"from\": 3692, \"to\": 3889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3877, \"end\": 3883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Garcia\", \"score\": 0.9999997316172444, \"rank\": 2.683827847511076e-07, \"text\": \"Garcia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Garcia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Garcia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 3701, \"to\": 3707}, {\"ngram\": \"a phone\", \"from\": 3713, \"to\": 3720}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 3735, \"to\": 3743}, {\"ngram\": \"real time\", \"from\": 3747, \"to\": 3756}, {\"ngram\": \"highlights\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 3772}, {\"ngram\": \"lowlights\", \"from\": 3778, \"to\": 3787}, {\"ngram\": \"social-media feeds\", \"from\": 3800, \"to\": 3818}, {\"ngram\": \"the feeling\", \"from\": 3820, \"to\": 3831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another possibility: People everywhere are becoming more selfish.\", \"from\": 3891, \"to\": 3956, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another possibility\", \"from\": 3891, \"to\": 3910}, {\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 3912, \"to\": 3918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Studies have shown that as countries get richer, their citizens become more individualistic.\", \"from\": 3957, \"to\": 4049, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Studies\", \"from\": 3957, \"to\": 3964}, {\"ngram\": \"countries\", \"from\": 3984, \"to\": 3993}, {\"ngram\": \"their citizens\", \"from\": 4006, \"to\": 4020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because good sportsmanship is largely about subordinating one's own emotions for the sake of the group, Matsumoto said, it follows that a decline in collectivist thinking could lead to more blowups.\", \"from\": 4050, \"to\": 4248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4154, \"end\": 4163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matsumoto_Domain\", \"score\": 0.998677155