e then, voicing doubts about elections has become contagious within the Republican Party.\", \"from\": 4445, \"to\": 4538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4521, \"end\": 4537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Dakota_Republican_Party\", \"score\": 0.7341019263357209, \"rank\": 0.36063080650428286, \"text\": \"Republican Party\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Dakota_Republican_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Dakota_Republican_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"doubts\", \"from\": 4465, \"to\": 4471}, {\"ngram\": \"elections\", \"from\": 4478, \"to\": 4487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the 2022 midterms, a raft of GOP candidatesrefused to concedetheir losses.\", \"from\": 4539, \"to\": 4616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4571, \"end\": 4574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republican_Party_of_Texas\", \"score\": 0.9995686584661834, \"rank\": 0.0004315276690397499, \"text\": \"GOP\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republican_Party_of_Texas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republican_Party_of_Texas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2022 midterms\", \"from\": 4542, \"to\": 4559}, {\"ngram\": \"concedetheir losses\", \"from\": 4596, \"to\": 4615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Trump has also rejected the court decisions against him-one jury found him civilly liable for sexual abuse, another criminally guilty of falsifying business records-as illegitimate.\", \"from\": 4617, \"to\": 4798, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4617, \"end\": 4622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.538762732590469e-14, \"text\": \"Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the court decisions\", \"from\": 4641, \"to\": 4660}, {\"ngram\": \"him-one jury\", \"from\": 4669, \"to\": 4681}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual abuse\", \"from\": 4711, \"to\": 4723}, {\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 4725, \"to\": 4732}, {\"ngram\": \"business records\", \"from\": 4765, \"to\": 4781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The generous take is that stubbornness is less about lying than about projecting strength.\", \"from\": 4799, \"to\": 4889, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The generous take\", \"from\": 4799, \"to\": 4816}, {\"ngram\": \"stubbornness\", \"from\": 4825, \"to\": 4837}, {\"ngram\": \"strength\", \"from\": 4880, \"to\": 4888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Hillary Clinton \\\"fought on\\\" in the 2008 primaries long past the point of having any chance of beating Barack Obama.)\", \"from\": 4890, \"to\": 5007, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4891, \"end\": 4906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hillary_Clinton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.606218681800602e-14, \"text\": \"Hillary Clinton\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hillary_Clinton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hillary_Clinton\"}, {\"begin\": 4993, \"end\": 5005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barack_Obama\", \"score\": 0.9999999973429112, \"rank\": 2.656614971537334e-09, \"text\": \"Barack Obama\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barack_Obama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barack_Obama\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2008 primaries\", \"from\": 4922, \"to\": 4940}, {\"ngram\": \"the point\", \"from\": 4951, \"to\": 4960}, {\"ngram\": \"any chance\", \"from\": 4971, \"to\": 4981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or perhaps it's theShaggy theoryof denial: Say it enough times, and people will believe it.\", \"from\": 5008, \"to\": 5099, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theShaggy theoryof denial\", \"from\": 5024, \"to\": 5049}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5076, \"to\": 5082}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From the November 2022 issue: Bad losers There is no L bigger than death, and we are trying to avoid that too.\", \"from\": 5101, \"to\": 5212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the November 2022 issue\", \"from\": 5106, \"to\": 5129}, {\"ngram\": \"Bad losers\", \"from\": 5131, \"to\": 5141}, {\"ngram\": \"no L\", \"from\": 5151, \"to\": 5155}, {\"ngram\": \"death\", \"from\": 5168, \"to\": 5173}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Venture-capital funds are investingbillionsin longevity research.\", \"from\": 5213, \"to\": 5278, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Venture-capital funds\", \"from\": 5213, \"to\": 5234}, {\"ngram\": \"investingbillionsin longevity research\", \"from\": 5239, \"to\": 5277}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rich people are paying to have themselvesfrozenwhen they die, and even if their body expires, AI promises topreservetheir digital self.\", \"from\": 5279, \"to\": 5414, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5373, \"end\": 5375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999981196197, \"rank\": 1.8803759068270765e-09, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rich people\", \"from\": 5279, \"to\": 5290}, {\"ngram\": \"themselvesfrozenwhen\", \"from\": 5310, \"to\": 5330}, {\"ngram\": \"their body\", \"from\": 5353, \"to\": 5363}, {\"ngram\": \"topreservetheir digital self\", \"from\": 5385, \"to\": 5413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We never have to say goodbye to our cultural idols, either: Thanks to hologram technology, we can watchAbbaandElvisand someday, probably, Post Malone in concert for the rest of our eternal life.\", \"from\": 5415, \"to\": 5609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5553, \"end\": 5564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Post_Malone\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.280638012437132e-39, \"text\": \"Post Malone\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Post_Malone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Post_Malone\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"goodbye\", \"from\": 5436, \"to\": 5443}, {\"ngram\": \"our cultural idols\", \"from\": 5447, \"to\": 5465}, {\"ngram\": \"hologram technology\", \"from\": 5485, \"to\": 5504}, {\"ngram\": \"concert\", \"from\": 5568, \"to\": 5575}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 5580, \"to\": 5588}, {\"ngram\": \"our eternal life\", \"from\": 5592, \"to\": 5608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In some contexts, there is beauty in refusing to accept loss.\", \"from\": 5611, \"to\": 5672, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some contexts\", \"from\": 5614, \"to\": 5627}, {\"ngram\": \"beauty\", \"from\": 5638, \"to\": 5644}, {\"ngram\": \"loss\", \"from\": 5667, \"to\": 5671}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Raging against the dying of the light can be moving, even inspiring.\", \"from\": 5673, \"to\": 5741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the dying\", \"from\": 5688, \"to\": 5697}, {\"ngram\": \"the light\", \"from\": 5701, \"to\": 5710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Death, be not proud,\\\" we say, ignoring the Grim Reaper's undefeated record.\", \"from\": 5742, \"to\": 5818, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Death\", \"from\": 5743, \"to\": 5748}, {\"ngram\": \"the Grim Reaper's undefeated record\", \"from\": 5782, \"to\": 5817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When it comes to sports, however, denying reality is not poetic; it's just dumb.\", \"from\": 5820, \"to\": 5900, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 5837, \"to\": 5843}, {\"ngram\": \"reality\", \"from\": 5862, \"to\": 5869}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletics is one of the few realms in life where the results are definitive.\", \"from\": 5901, \"to\": 5977, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngra